# Dual License

This project is available under a dual licensing model:

## 1. GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPLv3)

**Free for:**
- Open source projects
- Personal use
- Educational purposes
- Research and development

If you use this software in compliance with the AGPLv3, you must:
- Make your source code publicly available
- License your derivative works under AGPLv3
- Provide prominent notice of any modifications
- Include this license and copyright notice

Full AGPLv3 license text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

---

## 2. Commercial License

**Required for:**
- Proprietary/closed-source products
- Commercial applications that cannot comply with AGPLv3
- Products where you don't want to disclose source code
- Integration into non-GPL compatible software

For commercial licensing inquiries, please contact: cwthome@gmail.com

