## How to Choose

| Your Use Case | License Needed |
|---------------|----------------|
| Building an open source project | AGPLv3 (Free) |
| Personal learning/experimentation | AGPLv3 (Free) |
| Academic research | AGPLv3 (Free) |
| Selling a mobile app | Commercial License |
| Integrating into proprietary software | Commercial License |
| SaaS without releasing source code | Commercial License |

